      <div class="overflow-hidden">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pb-5 pt-20 sm:pt-30 lg:px-8 lg:pt-10">
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl gap-x-14 lg:mx-0 lg:flex lg:max-w-none lg:items-center">
            <div class="w-full max-w-xl lg:shrink-0 xl:max-w-2xl">
              <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">Home cooked meals, delivered to your door.</h1>
              <p class="relative mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 sm:max-w-md lg:max-w-none">I believe that food is not just about nourishment but also about creating a sense of community and connection.</p>
              <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-x-6">
                <a href="/checkout/calendar" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-orange-600 px-6 py-3 text-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out shadow-sm hover:bg-orange-500 hover:text-teal-800 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-orange-600">
                  <span class="mr-2">See the menu</span>
                  <a href="/about" class="text-md font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900 hover:text-teal-800">About Me <span aria-hidden="true">â†’</span></a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-14 flex justify-end gap-8 sm:-mt-44 sm:justify-start sm:pl-20 lg:mt-0 lg:pl-0">
                <div class="ml-auto w-44 flex-none space-y-8 pt-32 sm:ml-0 sm:pt-80 lg:order-last lg:pt-36 xl:order-none xl:pt-80">
                  <div class="relative">
                    <%= image_tag("riss-dish-coffee.png", alt: "local-ingredients", class: "aspect-[2/3] w-full rounded-xl bg-gray-900/5 object-cover shadow-lg") %>
                    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-900/10"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mr-auto w-44 flex-none space-y-8 sm:mr-0 sm:pt-52 lg:pt-36">
                  <div class="relative">
                    <%= image_tag("kale-salad.jpeg", class: "aspect-[2/3] w-full rounded-xl bg-gray-900/5 object-cover shadow-lg") %>
                    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-900/10"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="relative">
                    <%= image_tag("lobster-salad.jpeg", class: "aspect-[2/3] w-full rounded-xl bg-gray-900/5 object-cover shadow-lg") %>
                    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-900/10"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-44 flex-none space-y-8 pt-32 sm:pt-0">
                  <div class="relative">
                    <%= image_tag("garden.jpeg", class: "aspect-[2/3] w-full rounded-xl bg-gray-900/5 object-cover shadow-lg") %>
                    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-900/10"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="relative">
                    <%= image_tag("tuna.jpeg", class: "aspect-[2/3] w-full rounded-xl bg-gray-900/5 object-cover shadow-lg") %>
                    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-900/10"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
  <div class="overflow-hidden bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl md:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-start">
        <div class="px-6 lg:px-0 lg:pr-4 lg:pt-4">
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-lg">
            <dl class="mt-10 max-w-xl space-y-8 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 lg:max-w-none">
              <div class="relative pl-9">
                <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-orange-600">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.362 5.214A8.252 8.252 0 0112 21 8.25 8.25 0 016.038 7.048 8.287 8.287 0 009 9.6a8.983 8.983 0 013.361-6.867 8.21 8.21 0 003 2.48z" />
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18a3.75 3.75 0 00.495-7.467 5.99 5.99 0 00-1.925 3.546 5.974 5.974 0 01-2.133-1A3.75 3.75 0 0012 18z" />
                  </svg>
                  Nourish and Connect
                </dt>
                <hr class='pt-2'>
                <dd class="inline">Experience the power of food in its purest form - a home cooked meal from your neighborhood chef! Host a dinner party or just connect with your family over a classic dish.</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="relative pl-9">
                <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-orange-600">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 7.5v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0h-3m-2.25-4.125a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zM4 19.235v-.11a6.375 6.375 0 0112.75 0v.109A12.318 12.318 0 0110.374 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766z" />
                  </svg>
                  A Taste of Homemade Comfort
                </dt>
                <hr class='pt-2'>
                <dd class="inline">I know life gets busy and preparing wholesome meals can be challenging. I deliver comfort and flavor to your doorstep without the excess fees or packaging waste.</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="relative pl-9">
                <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-orange-600">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m0-10.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.75c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.57-.598-3.75h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.249-8.25-3.286zm0 13.036h.008v.008H12v-.008z" />
                  </svg>
                  Local, Fresh, and Organic
                </dt>
                <hr class='pt-2'>
                <dd class="inline">I prioritize local, fresh, and organic ingredients in every dish. My menu reflects my respect for quality, sustainability, and seasonality.</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sm:px-6 lg:px-0">
          <div class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-orange-500 px-6 pt-8 sm:mx-auto sm:max-w-2xl sm:rounded-3xl sm:pl-16 sm:pr-0 sm:pt-16 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none">
            <div class="absolute -inset-y-px -left-3 -z-10 w-full origin-bottom-left skew-x-[-30deg] bg-orange-100 opacity-20 ring-1 ring-inset ring-white" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl sm:mx-0 sm:max-w-none">
              <%= image_tag("riss-dish.jpeg", alt: "Product screenshot", class: "-mb-12 max-w-none rounded-tl-xl bg-gray-800 ring-1 ring-white/10") %>
            </div>
            <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 ring-1 ring-inset ring-black/10 sm:rounded-3xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="pt-20 pb-20 flex items-center justify-center">
    <a href="/checkout/calendar" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-orange-600 px-6 py-3 text-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out shadow-sm hover:bg-orange-500 hover:text-teal-800 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-orange-600">
      <span class="mr-2">Order a meal</span>
      <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-white pb-20 pt-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Previous Meals</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">Recipes and Musings from weeks past</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
        <% Product.all.each do |product| %>
          <article class="flex flex-col items-start justify-between">
            <div class="relative w-full">
              <%= image_tag url_for(product.main_image), class: "aspect-[16/9] w-full rounded-2xl bg-gray-100 object-cover sm:aspect-[2/1] lg:aspect-[3/2]" if product.main_image.attached? %>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-900/10"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="max-w-xl">
              <div class="mt-8 flex items-left text-xs">
                <time datetime="2020-03-16" class="text-gray-500"></time>
                <div class="flex-none self-end">
                  <% product.tags.each do |tag| %>
                    <dd class="text-left m-1 inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-amber-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-amber-700 ring-1 ring-inset ring-amber-600/20"><%= tag %></dd>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="group relative">
                <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900 group-hover:text-gray-600">
                  <span class="absolute inset-0"></span>
                  <%= product.title %>
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-5 line-clamp-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600"><%= product.description.truncate(150) %></p>
              </div>
              <!-- <div class="relative mt-8 flex items-center gap-x-4">
              <img src="riss-dish.jpeg" alt="" class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100">
              <div class="text-sm leading-6">
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  <a href="#">
                    <span class="absolute inset-0"></span>
                    Karissa Layden
                  </a>
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Head Chef</p>
              </div>
            </div> -->
            </div>
          </article>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="pt-20 pb-20 flex items-center justify-center">
    <a href="/checkout/calendar" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-orange-600 px-6 py-3 text-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out shadow-sm hover:bg-orange-500 hover:text-teal-800 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-orange-600">
      <span class="mr-2">Order a meal</span>
      <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
